	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You gain a second sort of awareness outside of yourself, seeing certain magical creatures in your mind, even when you aren't looking at them.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>You know if there is an &amp;reference[aberration]{Aberration}, &amp;reference[celestial]{Celestial}, &amp;reference[elemental]{Elemental}, &amp;reference[fey], &amp;reference[fiend]{Fiend}, or &amp;reference[undead] within 30 feet of you, as well as where the creature is located. Similarly, you know if there is a place or object within 30 feet of you that has been magically consecrated or desecrated (such as with the <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.TM7nuwiFhBjdE2MT]{Hallow} </em>spell). The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>This spell does not allow you to accurately see invisible creatures, but you know their location.</em></p>",
